 "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015534, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "There is no God but HE. There are no partners for Him in His Kingdom. There are none to challenge His Power. He counts all things in number, creates them and sets a pre-defined period for them. And all the seen and the unseen will be destroyed except His Face! To Him belongs the Decree and to Him is the return! Glory be to Him which has overcome everything by His Omnipotence, and has mastered them by His Power, and rules them by His Might!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "LAA ILAAHA ILLAA WAHDA-HU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU FEE MULKE-HI WA LAA MO-NAAZE-A’ LAHU FEE QUDRATE-HI AHSAA KULLA SHAIY-IN A’DADAN WA KHALAQA-HU WA JA-A’LA LAHU AMA-DAN (HADDAN) FA-KULLO MAA YORAA WA MAA LAA YORAA HAALE-KOON ILLAA WAJHA-HU LAHUL HUKMO WA ILAIY-HE TURJA-O’O-NA WA SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE LAZEE QAHARA KULLA SHAIY-IN BE-JABA-ROOTE-HI WAS-TAWLAA A’LAIY-HE BE-QUDRATE-HI WA MALAKA-HO BE-I’ZZATE-HI.", "ArabicText1": "لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَهٗ لَا شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ فِيْ مُلْكِهٖ وَلَا مُنَازِعَ لَهٗ فِيْ قُدْرَتِهٖ اَحْصٰى كُلَّ شَيْ‌ءٍ عَدَدًا وَخَلَقَهٗ وَجَعَلَ لَهٗ اَمَدًا (حَدًّا) فَكُلُّ مَا يُرٰى وَمَا لَا يُرٰى‌ هَالِكٌ اِلَّا وَجْهَهٗ لَهُ الْحُكْمُ وَاِلَيْهِ تُرْجَعُوْنَ‌ وَسُبْحَانَ اللهِ الَّذِيْ قَهَرَ كُلَّ شَيْ‌ءٍ بِجَبَرُوْتِهٖ وَاسْتَوْلٰى عَلَيْهِ بِقُدْرَتِهٖ وَمَلَكَهُ بِعِزَّتِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015535, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to my Creator while I was not nothing, supported me with His Mercy, fed me with His Blessings, extended His Bestowals on me, and favored me with His Guidance by inspiring me regarding His Oneness, acknowledging His Prophets (a.s) who carried His Message, and His Book revealed to the people as Proof to them. He is the God who did not question me for disbelief, and did not leave me to the enemies. He let me be of the descendants of the noblest of the Prophets (a.s) and helped me with the Seal of the Prophets (a.s).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "SUBHAANA KHAALE-QEE WA LAM AKO SHAIY-AL LAZEE KAFA-LANEE BE-RAHMATE-HI WA GHAZ-ZAANEE BE-NE’MATE-HI WA FASAHA LEE FEE A’TIY-YATE-HI WA MANNA A’LAIYYA BE-HIDAA-YATE-HI BE-MAA AL-HAMANEE MIN WAHDAA-NIYYATE-HI WAT-TASDEE-QE BE-AMBIYAA-E-HI WA HAAME-LEE RESAA-LATE-HI WA BE-KOTOBE-HIL MUN-ZALATE A’LAA BARIY-YATE-HIL MOOJA-BATE LE-HUJJATE-HIL LAZEE LAM YAKH-ZULNEE BE-JOHOO-DIN WA LAM YO-SALLIM-NEE ILAA A’NOO-DIN WAJA-A’LA MIN AKAA-REME AMBIYAA-E-HI SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIY-HIM AROO-MATEE WA MIN AFAA-ZELE-HIM NAB-A’TEE WA LEKHAA-TAME-HIM SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI A’W-NATEE.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ خَالِقِيْ وَلَمْ اَكُ شَيْئًا الَّذِيْ كَفَلَنِيْ بِرَحْمَتِهٖ وَغَذَّانِيْ بِنِعْمَتِهٖ وَفَسَحَ لِيْ فِيْ عَطِيَّتِهٖ وَمَنَّ عَلَيَّ بِهِدَايَتِهٖ بِمَا اَلْهَمَنِيْ مِنْ وَحْدَانِيَّتِهٖ وَالتَّصْدِيْقِ بِاَنْۢبِيَاۗئِهٖ وَحَامِلِيْ رِسَالَتِهٖ وَبِكُتُبِهِ الْمُنْزَلَةِ عَلٰى بَرِيَّتِهِ الْمُوْجِبَةِ لِحُجَّتِهِ الَّذِيْ لَمْ يَخْذُلْنِيْ بِجُحُوْدٍ وَلَمْ يُسَلِّمْنِيْ اِلٰى عَنُوْدٍ وَجَعَلَ مِنْ اَكَارِمِ اَنْۢبِيَاۗئِهٖ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِمْ اَرُوْمَتِيْ وَمِنْ اَفَاضِلِهِمْ نَبْعَتِيْ وَلِخَاتَمِهِمْ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهٖ عَوْنَتِيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015536, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! Please do not debase me after You honor me, do not lower my rank after You raise it, and do not leave me helpless after You give me victory. Please during this night forgive my sins, hear my prayers, and accept my deeds as indeed You have Power over all things. Please bestow blessings on the Prophet Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) and may His peace be on them plentifully.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA LAA TO-ZALLIL MINNEE MAA A’ZAZ-TA WA LAA TAZA’NEE BA’DA AN RAFA’TA WA LAA TAKH-ZULNEE BA’DA AN NASAR-TA WATWE FEE MATAA-WEE HAAZE-HIL LAIY-LATE ZONOO-BEE MAGH-FOO-RATAN WA AD-E’YA-TEE MASMOO-A’TAN WA QORO-BAATEE MAQBOO-LATAN FA-INNA-KA A’LAA KULLE SHAIY-IN QADEE-ROON WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN NABIYYE WA AALE-HI WA SALLAMA TASLEE-MAN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ لَا تُذَلِّلْ مِنِّيْ مَا اَعْزَزْتَ وَلَا تَضَعْنِيْ بَعْدَ اَنْ رَفَعْتَ وَلَا تَخْذُلْنِيْ بَعْدَ اَنْ نَصَرْتَ وَاطْوِ فِيْ مَطَاوِيْ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةِ ذُنُوْبِيْ مَغْفُوْرَةً وَاَدْعِيَتِيْ مَسْمُوْعَةً وَقُرُبَاتِيْ مَقْبُوْلَةً فَ اِنَّكَ عَلٰى‌ كُلِّ شَيْ‌ءٍ قَدِيْرٌ وَصَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ النَّبِيِّ وَآلِهٖ وَسَلَّمَ تَسْلِيْمًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1